{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":35,"Text":"故今日他在这里没有一个亲戚。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":36,"Text":"除脓汁外，他没有食物。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":37,"Text":"只有迷误的人们才吃脓汁。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":38,"Text":"不然！我以你们所能见的万象盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":39,"Text":"并且以你们不能见的幽玄盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":40,"Text":"这确是一个尊贵的使者的言辞，"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":41,"Text":"并不是诗人的言辞，你们很少信仰，"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":42,"Text":"也不是仆人的言辞，你们很少觉悟。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":43,"Text":"这是从全世界的主降示的。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":44,"Text":"假若他假借我的名义，捏造谣言，"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":45,"Text":"我必以权力逮捕他，"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":46,"Text":"然后必割断他的大动脉，"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":47,"Text":"你们中没有一个人能保卫他。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":48,"Text":"这确是对敬畏者的教训。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":49,"Text":"我的确知道你们中有否认的人。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":50,"Text":"这对于不信道的人们确是悔恨。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":51,"Text":"这确是真实的信念，"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":52,"Text":"故你当颂扬你的主的大名。"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"有人曾请求一种将发生的刑罚。"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"那是为不信的人们而预定的，没有任何人能加以抵抗。"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"那是安拉--天梯的主宰--发出的，"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"众天使和精神在一日之内升到他那里。那一日的长度是五万年。"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"你安然地忍受吧。"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"他们以为那刑罚是很远的，"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"我却以为那是很近的。"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"在那日天像熔铜，"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"山像彩绒。"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"亲戚相见不相问。"}]}